      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy again. The engine currently has a blown head gasket and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Externally, the car shows its age with extensive rust along the wheel wells and several large dents on the passenger side. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn and the electronics, including the radio and power windows, are non-functional. This is an ideal candidate for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a major restoration project or for someone in need of a donor vehicle for parts.",
