      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape for its next owner. It\u2019s super comfortable, fun to drive, and honestly has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so you\u2019re getting a great car at a fair price. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
