    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, renowned for its eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable damping rates. Crucially, the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells and the throttle actuators have been upgraded, addressing the primary mechanical concerns of the platform. It remains a mechanically sound specimen with sharp turn-in and a visceral, naturally aspirated soundtrack.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
